        {
            "+content": "Aya Oosawa was a gyaru high school student, who frequently visits a small record store. Not with the purpose of buying music, be with the purpose of meeting the store’s clerk. As Aya has developed a crush on the clerk, who has dark hair and wears a hoodie and a face mask. This individual seems to be the ideal love interest for Aya, only for there to be one problem, the clerk is in reality her nerdy female classmate Mitsuki Koga. <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
